snippet.title: Tennis On-Court - Official PSVR2 Release Window Announcement Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Get ready to serve in Tennis On-Court, which is coming to PSVR 2 this Fall. This trailer shows off gameplay from both the tennis court and the tennis club, with a variety of interiors and arena styles.

#SummerOfGaming
